data.meta_description: Charles Dance: Check out the list of all Charles Dance movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Charles Dance news on Times of India.
data.text:
Alastair Denniston misrepresented in 'Imitation Game': Family

PTI / Nov 29, 2014, 15:33 (IST)

Character of Alastair Denniston, played by Charles Dance in Benedict Cumberbatch starrer 'The Imitation Game' was not the 'baddie' and bully he is portrayed as in the movie, his grandchildren have said.

'Game of Thrones' to be made into a movie?

PTI / Nov 20, 2014, 15:42 (IST)

British actor Charles Dance, who played Tywin Lannister on TV drama 'Game of Thrones', has hinted that the fantasy story by JRR Martin may get a movie.

Christian Bale transforms into Frankenstein's monster for Maggie Gyllenhaal's 'The Bride'

etimes.in / Apr 05, 2024, 09:11 (IST)

Christian Bale embodies the Frankenstein monster in 'The Bride', alongside Jessie Buckley, Penelope Cruz, Peter Sarsgaard, and Annette Bening. The film, directed by Maggie Gyllenhaal, reimagines the classic tale in 1930s Chicago with a social twist. The film is slated to release on October 2, 2025.

Eva Green sues producers for $1 million over collapsed film

AP / Jan 27, 2023, 12:40 (IST)

A lawyer for Eva Green on Thursday accused producers of a collapsed film of trying to damage the performer's reputation by depicting her as a "diva."

Catherine de Medici in 'The Serpent Queen' is a modern anti-hero: creator Justin Haythe

PTI / Oct 17, 2022, 17:09 (IST)

Upcoming period drama 'The Serpent Queen' presents a "modern and unique anti-hero" in the lead character of Queen of France Catherine de Medici, says creator Justin Haythe. Starring Samantha Morton in the lead role, 'The Serpent Queen' tells the story of Catherine de Medici who, against all odds, became one of the most powerful and longest-serving rulers in French history.

'The Sandman' gets officially renewed for season 2

PTI / Nov 03, 2022, 11:12 (IST)

'The Sandman', the live-action adaptation of Neil Gaiman's popular graphic novel, has been renewed by a streaming service for the second season. According to the reports, news of the renewal leaked earlier on Wednesday via a since-deleted tweet from DC Comics, the publisher of the book. The formal announcement came in the evening.

Screen adaptation of Neil Gaiman's 'The Sandman' renewed for season 2

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Nov 03, 2022, 16:15 (IST)

The news of the renewal leaked online on November 2, 2022, and it was later formally announced in the evening. Read more details here.

'The King's Man' to release in India on December 31

PTI / Dec 01, 2021, 16:42 (IST)

Filmmaker Matthew Vaughn's upcoming directorial 'The King's Man' will debut in Indian theatres on December 31. The much-awaited spy drama, which was delayed multiple times due to the coronavirus pandemic.

Rhys Ifans on playing Lizard in 'Spider-Man: No Way Home' and being a 'big fan' of former co-star, late Irrfan Khan - Exclusive

etimes.in / Dec 24, 2021, 14:14 (IST)

Hollywood star Rhys Ifans has been winning praise for the villainous role of the Lizard in the Tom Holland-lead superhero film 'Spider-Man: No Way Home'.

The King’s Man trailer: Ralph Fiennes, Gemma Arterton starrer promises action and adventure

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Jun 22, 2020, 11:24 (IST)

Director Matthew Vaughn who brought to life ‘Kingsman: The Secret Service’ and it’s sequel ‘Kingsman: The Golden Circle’, is all set to turn back the clock and give fans a history lesson unlike any other with this action-packed prequel, ‘The King’s Man’.

Rhys Ifans and Tom Hollander on bringing their quirks to historical characters in Matthew Vaughn's 'The King's Man' - Exclusive!

etimes.in / Jan 13, 2022, 12:35 (IST)

Hollywood stars Rhys Ifans and Tom Hollander team up for the first time ever in filmmaker Matthew Vaughn's much-awaited 'The King's Man'. The spy drama, which saw multiple delays owing to the pandemic, will open in Indian cinema halls on Friday, January 14, 2022.

‘Godzilla: King of the Monsters’ box-office collection Day 3: The sci-fi monster film grosses Rs 4.50 crore on Saturday

TNN / Jun 02, 2019, 13:28 (IST)

The sci-fi monster film grossed Rs 4.50 crore on its third day on Saturday, taking its total collection at the box-office to Rs 10 crore nett, according o the report in BoxofficeIndia.com.

'The King's Man' director Matthew Vaughn confirms Colin Firth and Taron Egerton's return in 'Kingsman: The Blue Blood' - EXCLUSIVE!

etimes.in / Jan 14, 2022, 08:01 (IST)

'Kingsman' director Matthew Vaughn got candid with ETimes about bringing a fresh new perspective to the hit franchise with his all-new star-cast, outdoing himself with bold, brutal and bloody new action sequences, taking his franchise forward and even letting us in on the upcoming films including 'Kingsman: The Blue Blood'.

Game of Thrones actress Natalie Dormer wants to kiss the twin brother of on-screen nemesis!

TNN / Feb 27, 2016, 12:04 (IST)

Game of Thrones actress Natalie Dormer who plays the conniving yet kind Queen Margaery Tyrell has admitted a crush on Jamie Lannister, the twin brother and lover of the on-screen nemesis Cersei Lannister.

Emmys 2021 nominations list: 'The Crown,' 'Mandalorian', 'WandaVision' compete for top honours

TNN & Agencies / Jul 14, 2021, 09:19 (IST)

'The Crown' and 'The Mandalorian' led nominations on Tuesday for the Emmy Awards, the highest honours in television. The hit Marvel superhero series 'WandaVision' followed close behind earning 23 nominations, the most for a limited series.
